Introduction

Yiyeon is a South Korean rapper and singer. She is a former member of the girl group BVNDIT, and the group 1PS.

Yiyeon made her debut as the Leader of BVNDIT under MNH Entertainment with the release of their first single album, titled "BVNDIT, BE AMBITIOUS!", on April 10, 2019.

In 2015, Yiyeon was introduced as a member of Maroo Entertainment's girl group 1PS, under the stage name Dasol (which is also her birth name). However, she never actually debuted with them as the group disbanded sometime in the same year without any new release.
